{"tid":1287681,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾偉雄：「你喺網上講嘅嘢，都唔希望警方調查，係咪？」","createTime":"2019-07-05T10:11:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T17:21:22.000Z","uid":10014,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b27d0727ad2bb80842a9dd3c1bbb6a6e9b07f85c","tid":1287681,"uid":10014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T10:11:14.000Z","msg":"警務處處長曾偉雄，今日被記者問到警方會否主動調查，行政長官梁振英的女兒梁齊昕懷疑遭遇家暴的事件，曾偉雄回應稱，不是在網上說過的事情，警方就要調查：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「網上有好多嘢發生，有好多言論，不能就有關人士喺網上講過乜就去調查。就等於你喺網上講嘅嘢，都唔希望警方調查，係咪？」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n梁齊昕日前在社交媒體facebook，指控遭母親梁唐青儀以粗口辱罵和掌摑腳踢，又稱報警求助被阻止，後來警方到禮賓府，沒有立案就離開，外界質疑警方處理這宗懷疑家暴事件的手法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/齊昕fb稱被打-曾偉雄-不能網上講嘢就去查-親屬間暴力非家暴/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%BD%8A%E6%98%95fb%E7%A8%B1%E8%A2%AB%E6%89%93-%E6%9B%BE%E5%81%89%E9%9B%84-%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E8%AC%9B%E5%98%A2%E5%B0%B1%E5%8E%BB%E6%9F%A5-%E8%A6%AA%E5%B1%AC%E9%96%93%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E9%9D%9E%E5%AE%B6%E6%9A%B4%2F&d=dy0aigSTvaZIWgiFf%2BaM%2BH8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=4e4880b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%BD%8A%E6%98%95fb%E7%A8%B1%E8%A2%AB%E6%89%93-%E6%9B%BE%E5%81%89%E9%9B%84-%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E8%AC%9B%E5%98%A2%E5%B0%B1%E5%8E%BB%E6%9F%A5-%E8%A6%AA%E5%B1%AC%E9%96%93%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E9%9D%9E%E5%AE%B6%E6%9A%B4%2F&h=08304287\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/齊昕fb稱被打-曾偉雄-不能網上講嘢就去查-親屬間暴力非家暴/</a><br />\n<br />\n<code>我無嘢講 我要見律師 我唔解鎖電話 我唔簽任何文件 我要去醫院驗傷</code>"},{"pid":"71cb171818b55094e478a62a05c6a2ca08ebacd9","tid":1287681,"uid":10014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T17:14:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree